itemDescription: British aristocrat (1760-1825); daughter of David Murray, 2nd Earl of Mansfield; mother of George Finch-Hatton, 10th Earl of Winchilsea

wikipedia_page.main: Lady Elizabeth Mary Finch-Hatton (née Lady Elizabeth Mary Murray; 18 May 1760 – 1 June 1825) was a British aristocrat and the subject of a notable painting, once thought to be by Johann Zoffany, now attributed to David Martin.
